    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/1c5abfe4-1373-4f53-a111-1bd7de12279f> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/1c5abfe4-1373-4f53-a111-1bd7de12279f/resource/3233988b-1789-4d14-8928-36e5f091a935>;
