<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c671b9949a60f5e4638e5304f6e40442>.
<#c671b9949a60f5e4638e5304f6e40442> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U09910>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-04T06:22:43.202Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
