    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#byteSize> "1533"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#status> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/distribution-status/COMPLETED>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-04-03"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessURL> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/434>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Cykelmätningar (*.shp)"@sv, "Bicycle traffic measurements (*.shp)"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "En shapefil som innehåller cykelmätningar inom Gävle kommun. Attributdata:\n\nID (Site ID)\nNAME (Site name)\nADDRESS (Site address)\nDATEUPD (Datum som API-anropet gjordes)\nTIMEUPD (Klockslag enligt HHMMSS som API-anropet gjordes)\nLAT\nLONG\nPC_ID (Passage controller ID)\nPC_NAME (Passage controller name)\nPC_COUNT_T (Passage controller count today)\nPC_COUNT_Y (Passage controller count year)\n\nKoordinatsystemet är SWEREF 99 16 30."@sv, "A shapefile containing bicycle traffic measurements in Gävle Municipality.\n\nAttribute data:\n\nID (Site ID)\nNAME (Site name)\nADDRESS (Site address)\nDATEUPD (Date of API-call)\nTIMEUPD (Time of API-call in the format of HHMMSS)\nLAT\nLONG\nPC_ID (Passage controller ID)\nPC_NAME (Passage controller name)\nPC_COUNT_T (Passage controller count today)\nPC_COUNT_Y (Passage controller count year)\n\nThe coordinate system is SWEREF 99 16 30."@en;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0c15c897bc14d05534749c7386c6e46b>.
<#0c15c897bc14d05534749c7386c6e46b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/486>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-04T06:22:44.622Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#0c15c897bc14d05534749c7386c6e46b> {
<https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/486> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#downloadURL> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/485>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> "text/csv+zip";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2022-07-02"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#byteSize> "1915"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#status> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/distribution-status/COMPLETED>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-04-03"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessURL> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/485>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Statistics datasets (*.csv)"@en, "Statistik datamängder (*.csv)"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Two CSV files, one containing statistics for datasets published in a file format, and one for datasets published as WMS services.\n\nThe file statistik_filformat.csv contains information about the number of downloads for the file formats geojson, shape and CSV. Attribute data:\nDataset-ID (unique ID for the dataset)\nDataset (the dataset's name)\nGeoJSON (number of downloads in the geojson format)\nShapefile (number of downloads in the shape format)\nCSV (number of downloads in the CSV format)\nDate from (from which date downloads are counted)\nDate to (to which date downloads are counted)\nTotal (The sum of geojson, shape and CSV downloads)\n\nThe file statistik_wms.csv contains information about the number of requests that have been made to WMS services. Attribute data:\nWMS-ID (unique ID for the dataset)\nDataset (WMS) (the dataset's name)\nDate from (from which date requests are counted)\nDate to (to which date requests are counted)\nTotal (totalt number of requests)"@en, "Två stycken CSV-filer, en med statistik för datamängder i filformat, och en för de som är publicerade som WMS-tjänster.\n\nFilen statistik_filformat.csv innehåller information om antal nedladdningar för formaten geojson, shape och CSV. Attributdata:\nDataset-ID (unikt ID för datamängden)\nDataset (namn på datamängden)\nGeoJSON (antal nedladdningar i geojson-format)\nShapefile (antal nedladdningar i shape-format)\nCSV (antal nedladdningar i CSV-format)\nDate from (från vilket datum nedladdningar är räknade)\nDate to (till vilket datum nedladdningar är räknade)\nTotal (summan av geojson, shape och CSV nedladdningar)\n\nFilen statistik_wms.csv innehåller information om antal anrop mot WMS-tjänster. Attributdata:\nWMS-ID (unikt ID för datamängden)\nDataset (WMS) (namn på datamängden)\nDate from (från vilket datum anrop är räknade)\nDate to (till vilket datum anrop är räknade)\nTotal (totalt antal anrop)"@sv;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution>
}

